You: that sucks
Stranger: :P

Stranger: that sucks

ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (02:55): I'm gonna do Middle Eastern studies at college in fact
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (02:55): what sparked your interest in that?
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (02:56): I wanna work in the CIA

ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (02:57): and I already know three languages fluently, so I figure if I get another high worth language like Arabic and some relevant middle east knowledge i might have a good chance
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (02:57): also I love the history of the middle east
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (02:59): Do you consider yourself Arabian?
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (02:59): I know thats a bit of an issue in the middle east
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (03:00): But you're not, you're Egyptian
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (03:00): what's your take on the war in iraq?
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (03:00): Egyptians didn't consider themselves as "Arabian" until the government started pushing the agenda in like the 1930s
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (03:00): I speak arabic, I consider myself arabian

ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (03:01): I think its sad people consider themselves Arabian when they are from a countries which have far richer histories than Arabia. The Arabians were just some tribesmen before Mohammed came along, Arabia can't compare to the histories of Egypt, Iraq, Iran, Lebanon etc
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (03:01): half of my family comes from egypt, my dad's side that's why I say I'm from there, other half is from yemen
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (03:02): yemenis are considered the epitome of arabians haha
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (03:02): do you personally know people from yemen?
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (03:03): and have you ever been to yemen?
80e393251de0803f67440fb35878d225 (03:03): if not, you're being really prejudice
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (03:03): The country sucks, they can't keeo control of their country
ea4d7b558d0b319d287b41894769a579 (03:03): all the terrorists are training there
